}  \\
\glll {}  S  {}  V  V  V  A  {}  P  V \\  
{} Qau  a  ta  ewar  mis.  Mis-an  a  ta  man  pi'i.\\
{} good  3\textsc{sg}  \textsc{top} return  sit  sit-\textsc{real} 3\textsc{sg}  \textsc{top} grass  twine\\
